WEBVTT

00:02.040 --> 00:04.399
A streetwalker, Sir, found ripped.

00:08.080 --> 00:09.359
This man once called me a friend.

00:09.360 --> 00:10.919
And then, amongst others,

00:10.920 --> 00:12.479
you killed his brother.

00:12.480 --> 00:14.999
Well, you know, he was never
one to hold a grudge.

00:15.000 --> 00:16.079
Stop!

00:16.079 --> 00:17.279
Who is it tells me?

00:17.280 --> 00:18.320
Police!

00:19.800 --> 00:22.279
If I decide to finish with that life?

00:22.280 --> 00:24.119
Then, you must be brave, Rose,

00:24.120 --> 00:25.640
and look for another.

00:30.120 --> 00:31.479
Always were a faker.

00:33.080 --> 00:35.360
This man's rooms, now!

00:37.320 --> 00:38.519
Another tart's been ripped

00:38.520 --> 00:41.240
and I've a snitch sends me to you!

00:42.920 --> 00:44.280
Take him!

00:47.560 --> 00:49.319
The boy was crippled,

00:49.320 --> 00:51.600
then put into the water to drown.

